      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "from datetime import datetime\nimport random\n\nnow = datetime.now()\ndate_str = now.strftime(\"%m/%d/%Y\")\ntime_str = now.strftime(\"%H:%M\")\n\ncharacter = random.choice([\n    \"Cheerful Girl in Pink\", \n    \"Tiny Mermaid Girl\", \n    \"Adorable Elf Girl\", \n    \"Joyful Princess\", \n    \"Cute Wizard Girl\", \n    \"Playful School Girl\"\n])\n\nYoutube_Channel_Url = \"https://youtube.com/@algonovalabs?si=p6UJAPdolW5Mfdq5\"\nYoutube_Channel_name = \"AlgoNova Labs\"\nImage_URL = _input.first().json.webViewLink\nYoutube_Video_Url = f\"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/{_('Get many videos').first().json.id.videoId}\"\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"\nIMPORTANT:\nYou MUST use the exact YouTube video URL and channel URL provided below.\nDo NOT modify them, do NOT guess them, do NOT generate new ones.\n\nVideo URL (use EXACTLY this):\n{Youtube_Video_Url}\n\nChannel URL (use EXACTLY this):\n{Youtube_Channel_Url}\n\nCreate highly engaging posts for:\n• Facebook\n• Instagram\n• X (Twitter) — max 280 characters, no images\n• YouTube Community — must include both video + channel links\n\nTheme: whimsical, magical, pastel, FOMO-driven like {Youtube_Channel_name}.  \nPromote the new video magically.\n\nProvide 5 creative variations per platform.\nEach variation must:\n1. Be short, magical, whimsical, and FOMO-driven.\n2. Use emojis and interaction hooks.\n3. Include BOTH the Video URL and Channel URL EXACTLY as given.\n4. Be unique for every variation and platform.\n5. X post must stay under 280 chars and NOT reference images.\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (MANDATORY):\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this structure.\nUse the FIRST variation of each platform as default:\n\n{{\n  \"Date\": \"{date_str}\",\n  \"Time\": \"{time_str}\",\n  \"Facebook Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE\",\n  \"Instagram Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE\",\n  \"X Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE (must include both links, <280 chars)\",\n  \"Youtube Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE. Watch till the end! {Youtube_Channel_name}: {Youtube_Channel_Url}\",\n  \"Image URL\": \"{Image_URL}\",\n  \"Status\": \"Ready to Post\",\n  \"Category\": \"Community Engagement\",\n  \"Notes\": \"Include 5+ creative variations per platform. Use hashtags #AlgoNovaMagic #PastelWorld #WhimsicalVibes.\"\n}}\n\nRULES:\n- DO NOT change or create any YouTube links.\n- Do NOT invent URLs.\n- ONLY use the provided Video URL and Channel URL EXACTLY as given.\n- Do NOT use asterisks (**), dashes (-), or Markdown-style symbols in any post.\n- Output must be valid JSON without formatting symbols or markdown.\n\"\"\"\n\nreturn {'chatInput': prompt}\n"
