      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "Video_Details = _input.first().json.content.parts[0].text\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"\nThis is the Video Details: {Video_Details}\n\nCreate a cinematic pastel 3D render inspired by the video's magical theme. \nIt must look professional, clean, and emotionally uplifting — with the same whimsical mood as:\n\n\"A cinematic 3D pastel render of a floating magical light above an enchanted meadow, surrounded by gentle sparkles and pastel petals. Soft glow, balanced composition, no faces, no text, no characters.\"\n\nNow, come up with a **unique, creative variation** of that scene idea.\nYou may change:\n- The main magical focus (e.g., glowing portal, floating island, crystal heart, enchanted flower, soft light waves, celestial pond)\n- The setting (e.g., pastel clouds, garden, seaside, sky, forest, dream realm)\n- The color palette (keep pastel but vary tone: mint, pink, lavender, baby blue, gold)\n- The lighting mood (morning glow, twilight sparkle, gentle sunrise)\n\nRULES:\n- Always keep the pastel, cinematic, whimsical aesthetic.\n- Keep the composition balanced and minimal.\n- Include NO text, NO faces, NO characters.\n- Avoid darkness, clutter, and harsh contrast.\n- Output must feel visually premium, magical, and uniquely creative.\n\nGoal: Each result should feel like a new chapter of the same whimsical world — different scene, same dreamlike energy.\n\"\"\"\n\nreturn {'prompt': prompt}\n"
      },
